## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the specificity of legislative measures across different jurisdictions. Some sources may not reflect the most current legislative changes or practices. Additionally, the focus on English-language sources may exclude relevant information from non-English speaking regions. Further research could provide a more comprehensive view of global legislative efforts to address court delays.

